    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a restoration project or for parts. The exterior paint is heavily faded with several noticeable dents and significant rust patches along the rocker panels. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and the electronics are largely non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs but suffers from a persistent knock and a leaking transmission, meaning it will likely need to be towed. It is an honest project for someone with the time and resources to bring it back to life.",
